affixes.name: Tyrannical
affixes.description: Bosses have 30% more health. Bosses and their minions inflict up to 15% increased damage.

affixes.name: Raging
affixes.description: Non-boss enemies enrage at 30% health remaining, dealing 75% increased damage until defeated.

affixes.name: Volcanic
affixes.description: While in combat, enemies periodically cause gouts of flame to erupt beneath the feet of distant players.

affixes.name: Tormented
affixes.description: Servants of the Jailer can be found throughout the dungeon and grant powerful boons when defeated. If a servant is not dealt with, they empower the final boss.
